Ya, tentu saja.

87
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:05,665
Astaga.

88
00:09:06,499 --> 00:09:09,085
Namun, bukankah jabatan itu
sudah diisi orang lain?

89
00:09:09,877 --> 00:09:11,754
Mungkin saja besok lowong.

90
00:09:14,882 --> 00:09:16,509
Dasar cerdik.

91
