93
00:09:21,722 --> 00:09:22,974
Biar aku carikan perawan...

94
00:09:26,018 --> 00:09:27,145
Melihat sikapmu ini,

95
00:09:27,228 --> 00:09:30,898
pantas kariermu tidak pernah maju.

96
00:09:31,190 --> 00:09:33,526
Kau bisa kosongkan posisi
yang terisi dengan paksa

97
00:09:33,609 --> 00:09:36,487
dan menyingkirkan suami orang jika ada.

98
00:09:37,697 --> 00:09:40,658
Benar sekali. Sekarang, minumlah

99
00:09:40,741 --> 00:09:44,120
agar aku bisa menuangkan
minuman lagi untukmu.

100
00:10:20,990 --> 00:10:22,074
Lihat apa kau?

101
00:10:24,327 --> 00:10:25,703
Langit, Tuan.

102
00:10:26,579 --> 00:10:27,914
Kenapa melihat ke langit?

103
00:10:30,208 --> 00:10:35,171
Aku memikirkan alasan seekor burung hitam
bisa merusak pemandangan langit.

104
00:10:37,173 --> 00:10:38,466
Kau budak keluarga mana?

105
00:10:40,927 --> 00:10:42,178
Kenapa Tuan bertanya?

106
00:10:42,803 --> 00:10:44,764
Matamu harus tertuju ke tanah.

107
00:10:45,389 --> 00:10:46,849
Langit terlalu tinggi untukmu.

108
00:10:47,725 --> 00:10:49,727
Jika budak melihat atau membidik tinggi,

109
00:10:50,394 --> 00:10:51,938
